Country furniture styles convey a sense of simple comfort and the warmth of hearth and home. While some country furniture can be rustic, the pieces included in Traditional Country Furniture are of quality construction and design, drawing from the best of traditional American furniture styles. Each furniture piece includes step-by-step photos and instructions, with a variety of skill levels represented.

Projects include:

Kentucky sideboard
Blanket chest
Country wall 
shelf
Tavern table
Burlington Farmer's Desk
Drop-leaf kitchen table
Tall clock
and more!


By Popular Woodworking Editors
Published by F+W Media in 2013
